posting_body: ['Welcome home to The Eddy', 'The Eddy is located along the waterfront in East Boston, boasting unrivaled views of the Boston skyline and within walking distance to an eclectic mix of restaurants, shops and entertainment.', "The Eddy is transit-oriented and serves as a bridge between Boston's most vibrant neighborhoods.", 'Pricing and availability subject to change.', 'Call Now:', '(617) 380-4884 x 17', 'OR Text', '17', 'to', '(617) 380-4884', 'to text with us.', 'Follow This Link for More Information:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 597.0 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Low-flow fixtures', '- Nest Learning Thermostats™', '- High-efficiency LED lighting', '- Energy Star-rated appliances', '- Locally-sourced and recycled-content materials', '- Well-designed living spaces', 'Community Amenities', '- Poolside restaurant service for residents', '- Outdoor terrace', "- Lounge with a chef's kitchen", '- Access to a new waterfront park', '- Car sharing options', '- Sun deck', '- Fireplace', '- Direct access to Lo Presti Park', '- Secure bike parking', '- Music room', '- On-site restaurant with indoor and outdoor dining spaces', '- Bike maintenance facilities', '- Rooftop deck with seating and 270° views', '- Waterfront property with uninterrupted views of the Boston Harbor and city skyline', '- Pet-friendly', '- Access to boat landing', '- Grilling stations', '- Well-served by transit through the blue line, an expanded water taxi station, highways and Logan Airport', '- Pool', '- Dog wash', '- Private conference rooms', '- Modern fitness facilities', 'The Eddy', '10 New Street , East Boston, MA, 02128', 'EsuX5962evvq']
